kismat is a 1968 indian hindi film directed by manmohan desai . the film was directed by manmohan desai and produced by &lt;unk&gt; malhotra . the film stars biswajeet , helen , kamal mehra , helen , kamal mehra , helen , kamal mehra , helen , kamal mehra , helen , kamal mehra , helen , kamal mehra , helen , kamal mehra , om shivpuri , om prakash mehra , om prakash and babita . the film was remade in hindi as kismat ( 1968 ) .